{
  "stem": "7832.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But today, I am very grateful that she did that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so we were-- I was up at 5:00, and my grandmother taught me whatever she felt that I should know at that time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I had this constant argument with her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I don't have to do this at 5 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she says, you have to do that, because when you get married, you're going to have to do that for your family.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I used to say to her, but I'm going to get somebody to do that for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she used to say, but you're going to have to know how to do it in order to show the other person how to do it, whoever is going to do it for you.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And today, I remember those words, and they're so true.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so we were busy all morning, baking and preparing for Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Of course, I went to school, and by the time I came back, it was time to make the cholent.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the cholent was something that my father and my grandfather and my grandmother worked together, because each one liked different things in the cholent.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My father liked corn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So he roasted the corn in the oven after my grandmother finished baking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then he chopped it in one of those old-fashioned-- I don't know what they call it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But in Jewish, they call it a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They-- they-- they, like, kind of pounded it to pieces.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So my father did that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And my grandfather liked barley, So he used to pick out the bad barley from the barley to prepare that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And of course, my grandmother did the rest of the stuff.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
